
            Video
            Fake me: Can you become an Instagram influencer in a week?
            Kenyan social media sceptic Joey agrees to live her life on Instagram for a week to see what happens.But can she remain true to herself when the line between real and fake starts to blur? This is part of a series by the BBC on disinformation and fake news - a global problem challenging the way we share information and perceive the world around us.To see more stories and learn more about the series visit www.bbc.co.uk/fakenews. 
                
                        12 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
